 <!-- What are Events in JavaScript?
Events wo actions hote hain jo user karta hai ya web page mein automatically hote hain. Jaise:

Button click karna

Mouse le jaana kisi element ke upar

Keyboard se key press karna

Page load hona

JavaScript use karta hai event listeners jo yeh dekhte hain ki koi event hua ya nahi, aur fir uske response mein koi function run karte hain.

ðŸŽ¯ Real-Life Example:
Socho tum ek doorbell ho. Jab koi button dabata hai (event), tum tring tring bajti ho (function call hota hai).
ðŸ‘‰ Yahaan button dabana = event
ðŸ‘‰ tring tring = JavaScript function

ðŸ“¦ Common Events:
Event Name	Kab hota hai
onclick	Jab element pe click hota hai
onmouseover	Jab mouse le jaate ho element ke upar
onmouseout	Jab mouse nikalte ho element se
onkeydown	Jab keyboard ki press hoti hai
onload	Jab page pura load ho jata hai

